snippet.title: Sail your Way: Recruit Legends, Become a Legend
snippet.description:
Ahoy, Adventurers!
Sail your way in Sea of Conquest! Recruit heroes and grow your fleet!

- Customize your ship cabins to your likings
- Build your roaster of heroes to aid you in your conquest
- Carve out your legacy and rise as a legend of the seas!
Arrgh! Dive into the Adventure!
    
🏴‍☠️ Join the Pirates' Gang for a more thrilling journey!  🏴‍☠️
Discord: https://discord.gg/347tWdEy2k
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/people/Sea-of-Conquest/100083472589598/
X: https://twitter.com/seaofconquest
